     FABBWP69 IF  E           K        DISK
     FABBWP69AO   F    1100            DISK
      *--------------------------------------------------
     E                    MTH     1  12  3
      *--------------------------------------------------
     I           SDS
     I                                        1   8 #PGM
     I                                      244 253 #WSID
     I                                      254 263 #USER
     I* SYSTEM TIME
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140WSDT
